  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/92551161809a554c84cfc75aff6518e3.avif?t=1766836517\" width=800 height=80 /></span>You’ve accepted a mysterious job from a random person, agreeing to participate in a scientific drug trial in an abandoned facility deep in the forest. Your task? Navigate through three mazes while testing substances that distort your perception and impair your abilities. Each pill you take brings you a step closer to the truth, blurring the line between reality and hallucination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/51e568ca197e367e9b17cd24407e27e0.poster.avif?t=1766836517\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/51e568ca197e367e9b17cd24407e27e0.webm?t=1766836517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/51e568ca197e367e9b17cd24407e27e0.mp4?t=1766836517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/10835fa676f5e080cb50da55e90c6427.avif?t=1766836517\" width=800 height=80 /></span>With each pill, the mazes become more dangerous and your perception less reliable. You’ll feel the weight of isolation and paranoia as the environment twists and turns around you. The facility holds secrets, and the environment is willing to threaten you. Can you uncover the purpose of this experiment, or will you lose yourself in the darkness? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/849e46b9c8c08362d42539c0f05b7cda.poster.avif?t=1766836517\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/849e46b9c8c08362d42539c0f05b7cda.webm?t=1766836517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/849e46b9c8c08362d42539c0f05b7cda.mp4?t=1766836517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/e6498401f7c7460863d20008256f8aba.avif?t=1766836517\" width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's not just regular thinking required for your survival; good listening-skills are a must too. The substances you’re testing alter your perception, making every sound a potential warning or a cruel trick of the mind. Hallucinations creep into your senses, intensifying the risk of panic and even heart failure. Randomly placed closets and ladders offer brief respite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/57d8e0a9cc8d50ca37594bd88b6d566e.poster.avif?t=1766836517\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/57d8e0a9cc8d50ca37594bd88b6d566e.webm?t=1766836517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/57d8e0a9cc8d50ca37594bd88b6d566e.mp4?t=1766836517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Environment:</strong> Get used to the changing environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong> Shape the outcome based on your choice.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hiding System:</strong> Remember specific hiding spots and hide when in danger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Gameplay:</strong> Navigate through the mazes without getting lost.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Sound Design:</strong> Pay attention to the sounds around you, indicating whether you are in danger or not.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Tension:</strong> Are you ready to withhold a place where hallucinations blur the line between reality and fear?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional Information:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It is recommended to play at max settings, post-processing and headphones for the best experience!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game was made by one person and without the use of AI, it may appear short, but I will expand it with updates in the future.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/2f3b3b578b6fddb7ad67407bb96a8377.avif?t=1766836517\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras_big/2f3b3b578b6fddb7ad67407bb96a8377.webp?t=1766836517 width=1560 height=723 /></span></p>",
