\" ><strong>Dynamic Environment:</strong> Get used to the changing environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong> Shape the outcome based on your choice.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hiding System:</strong> Remember specific hiding spots and hide when in danger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Gameplay:</strong> Navigate through the mazes without getting lost.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Sound Design:</strong> Pay attention to the sounds around you, indicating whether you are in danger or not.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Tension:</strong> Are you ready to withhold a place where hallucinations blur the line between reality and fear?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional Information:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It is recommended to play at max settings, post-processing and headphones for the best experience!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game was made by one person and without the use of AI, it may appear short, but I will expand it with updates in the future.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras/2f3b3b578b6fddb7ad67407bb96a8377.avif?t=1766836517\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439210/extras_big/2f3b3b578b6fddb7ad67407bb96a8377.webp?t=1766836517 width=1560 height=723 /></span></p>",
